Parallelize API calls & add transliterated TTS support

- Rewrote query.py to use asyncio.gather for concurrent RAG search,
  Bright Data SERP, and gov data enrichment calls
- Wrapped all sync service calls with asyncio.to_thread
- Added transliterate_text method to translator.py using Azure
  Translator /transliterate endpoint with script mappings for all 11
  Indian languages
- Added answer_romanized field to QueryResponse schema
- Frontend TTS now speaks romanized Latin text via English voice when
  transliteration succeeds, falls back to native-language TTS otherwise
- transliterate_text returns None (not original text) on failure,
  preventing English TTS from speaking native-script text
- Added ur/as to SCRIPT_RANGES for complete language coverage
- Fixed BrokenPipeError handling in proxy server
- Updated replit.md with parallelization and transliteration docs
